        "created_at": "2024-02-20T01:17:50.241Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=4916152&amp;iNote=10985848\"><b>1973 Domaine Marc Morey &amp; Fils Chassagne-Montrachet</b></a> - France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Chassagne-Montrachet (2/18/2024)<br>\nA fresh colour. Superb nose of struck match, preserved lemon, apricot, white peach and spice. The palate has a strong imprint of citrus and rind characters. It has vinous sweetness and fabulous minerally line. Each sip invites another and it is complex, engaging and simply brilliant for its level.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/\">CellarTracker</a></p>",
